latestPosts.caption:
Thankyou for accepting me as your sister and not as bhabhi ❤️ i always looked upto you , chhavi and vansh for everything . I have only one regret that I’ve spent very less time with you !! For world our relation was devar and bhabhi but no one knows we always saw each other as our own blood . I have no words to explain my pain . All i know is our lives will never be same without you ! We will miss you every moment . I can’t believe that I won’t be waking u up everyday now , ordering snacks for u and hiding it from mom . If there’s another life . I will choose you as my brother all over again . Thankyou for always supporting me and understanding me ❤️ I don’t know when i will recover from this loss . Whenever i am closing my eyes i see your smiling face 💔
Until we meet again ( our golgappa ) ❤️
Love you so much and miss you alot ❤️😘
